        "action": "Require fuel outlets to display the cost of fuel per gallon",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Require fuel retailers to clearly display petrol and diesel prices in cost per gallon. Vehicle fuel consumption figures in the British Isles are most usually given in miles per gallon. We believe the existing pricing displays, ie cost per litre, disguises the cost to motorists of buying fuel.",
